{"tid":1682370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林X月娥中學時期豔照流出(多圖)","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:05:26.000Z","uid":58983,"like":13,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"48a327af248efaf6ca8958331fe7a6d2ac9c597f","tid":1682370,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我呃左大家入黎，我係仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，香港人抗爭日程表facebook專頁和IG帳號推出咗啦！<br />\n我哋係「香港人抗爭日程表文宣頻道」telegram channel嘅延伸，fb版本和IG版本。<br />\n有鑑於近期活動宣傳不足 ，遊行人數日漸減少，我哋希望可以加強文宣，呼籲更多香港人出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋讓冇telegram但係有facebook或IG的手足同樣收到各區活動嘅消息（尤其是上年紀的手足們）。歡迎大家透過facebook和IG平台上分享日程表文宣。<br />\n如果大家認同，麻煩請follow及share啦，感謝！<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\nFB Link: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%A1%A8-103001221140027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8-103001221140027&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt34PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=17f5320f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%A1%A8-103001221140027</a><br />\nIG:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkschedulepromo?igshid=1ece2lrjj548n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkschedulepromo%3Figshid%3D1ece2lrjj548n&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt34PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=5d96d1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkschedulepromo?igshid=1ece2lrjj548n</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b03022dd5a6ccfc904a4bf86cc6af993d2620c","tid":1682370,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"95d5979